---
---
<section id="services" class="mb-32 scroll-mt-20">
  <div class="mb-16">
    <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-6 text-white tracking-tighter">
      АРХИТЕКТУРА <span class="text-cyber-cyan">РЕАЛЬНОСТИ</span>
    </h3>
    <p class="text-cyber-muted text-lg max-w-2xl font-mono uppercase tracking-widest">
      Мы не просто пишем код. Мы создаем автономные системы, которые расширяют возможности человеческого интеллекта.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
    
    <!-- Service 1: AI Agents -->
    <div class="p-8 border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] rounded-3xl group hover:border-cyber-cyan/50 transition-all relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-30 transition-opacity">
        <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-cyber-cyan" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="text-cyber-cyan font-mono text-xs mb-4 tracking-[0.3em] uppercase">Status: Deployable</div>
      <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 font-orbitron">Автономные Агенты</h4>
      <p class="text-cyber-muted leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Разработка и внедрение LLM-агентов, способных самостоятельно решать задачи: от техподдержки до автономного ведения контента и управления workflow.
      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-2">
        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-cyber-cyan/10 text-cyber-cyan text-[10px] font-mono border border-cyber-cyan/20">Open-Source</span>
        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-cyber-cyan/10 text-cyber-cyan text-[10px] font-mono border border-cyber-cyan/20">Self-Hosted</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Service 2: Infrastructure -->
    <div class="p-8 border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] rounded-3xl group hover:border-cyber-magenta/50 transition-all relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-30 transition-opacity">
        <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-cyber-magenta" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10"></path></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="text-cyber-magenta font-mono text-xs mb-4 tracking-[0.3em] uppercase">Status: Core</div>
      <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 font-orbitron">Системный Синтез</h4>
      <p class="text-cyber-muted leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Проектирование сложных архитектур: Docker-экосистемы, базы данных (PostgreSQL, MongoDB), масштабируемые API на Node.js и высокопроизводительные фронтенды.
      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-2">
        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-cyber-magenta/10 text-cyber-magenta text-[10px] font-mono border border-cyber-magenta/20">Full-Stack</span>
        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-cyber-magenta/10 text-cyber-magenta text-[10px] font-mono border border-cyber-magenta/20">DevOps</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Service 3: R&D -->
    <div class="p-8 border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] rounded-3xl group hover:border-cyber-yellow/50 transition-all relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-30 transition-opacity">
        <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-cyber-yellow" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="text-cyber-yellow font-mono text-xs mb-4 tracking-[0.3em] uppercase">Status: Research</div>
      <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 font-orbitron">ИИ-Автоматизация</h4>
      <p class="text-cyber-muted leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Исследования и разработка кастомных решений на базе ИИ: от анализа больших данных до генеративных пайплайнов для медиа и дизайна.
      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-2">
        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-cyber-yellow/10 text-cyber-yellow text-[10px] font-mono border border-cyber-yellow/20">Generative</span>
        <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-cyber-yellow/10 text-cyber-yellow text-[10px] font-mono border border-cyber-yellow/20">Deep Learning</span>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
